Darcs::Notify
-------------

Darcs::Notify compares the list of patches in a darcs repository
against a saved backup copy and sends emails about the changes.

For full documentation, run:
  perldoc darcs-notify

Installation
------------

To build, test and install:

 perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install

